title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 28 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 28 2022
description:
Clay and Buck send their thoughts to everyone in the path of Hurricane Ian. "Where's Jackie?" Biden looks around for dead congresswoman. Governor DeSantis prepares Florida for hurricane. Biden caves, finally calls Governor DeSantis. Whodunit? Russia's Nord Stream pipeline is sabotaged. Biden vowed to "end" the pipeline if Putin invaded Ukraine.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
